      <section id="welcome">
        <h2>Welcome to Preventive Dental - Your Team in Reading, PA</h2>
        <p>
          Going to the dentist shouldn't be complicated. With us, it won't be. Whether you need reliable care for a
          painful tooth or long-term maintenance to keep your smile healthy, we'll handle it with care and
          professionalism.
        </p>
        <p>
          We treat what's necessary and explain everything clearly so you'll always know what's happening and why. We
          care about your comfort and make sure you feel informed and in control.
        </p>
        <p>Whether it's a filling, or a dental emergency, you'll get honest care you can trust.</p>
        <p>
          <em
            >Trusted by patients in <strong>Reading, PA</strong> for over 20 years because good dental care starts with
            trust.</em
          >
        </p>
      </section>
      <!-- TOOTHACHE SECTION -->
      <section id="toothache">
        <h2>Got a Toothache?</h2>
        <p>We fix those.</p>
        <p>
          Whether it just started or it's been lingering, we're here to help. You've got options. We'll walk you through
          each one, so you stay in control. We'll explain what's going on, what we can do, and how to make it better.
          Often the same day.
        </p>
        <p>No pressure. No surprises. Just dental care that makes sense.</p>

        <h3>Here's What You Can Expect:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Straightforward answers. No confusing terms</li>
          <li>Treatment options laid out clearly. You choose</li>
          <li>A calm, respectful experience from start to finish</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Feel Better, Starting Today</h3>
        <p>Call or text. We'll get you in, talk it through, and take care of what hurts. Simple as that.</p>

        <div class="cta-wrapper">
          <a href="tel:+16106785700" class="cta" onclick="gtag('event', 'click_call_now');"> 📞 Call Now </a>
          <a href="sms:+16106785700" class="cta" onclick="gtag('event', 'click_text_now');"> 📱 Text Now </a>
        </div>
        <p class="phone-number">+1 (610) 678-5700</p>
      </section>

      <!-- OPTIONAL CONTENT SECTION -->
      <section id="optional-content" style="display: none"></section>

      <!-- WHAT'S BOTHERING YOU SECTION -->
      <section id="whats-bothering-you">
        <h2>What's Bothering You?</h2>
        <p>
          Not sure if you need a dentist? Just know something feels off? You're not alone. These are the kinds of things
          we help people with every single day:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Toothache</strong> - sharp, throbbing, or just won't go away</li>
          <li><strong>Bleeding gums</strong> when you brush or floss</li>
          <li><strong>Bad breath</strong> that keeps coming back</li>
          <li><strong>Swollen jaw or face</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Cracked or chipped tooth</strong> from biting something hard</li>
          <li><strong>Food always getting stuck</strong> between the same teeth</li>
          <li><strong>Sensitivity</strong> to hot, cold, or sweet things</li>
          <li><strong>Loose crown or filling</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Gum bump or sore</strong> that won't go away</li>
          <li><strong>Missing teeth</strong> making it hard to chew or smile confidently</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Whatever it is, we'll take a look, explain what's going on, and talk through your options. You stay in
          control. We'll just help make sense of it.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- OUR APPROACH SECTION -->
      <section id="our-approach">
        <h2 class="centered-text">
          ✨<br />
          What Makes Us Different
        </h2>
        <p>
          We focus on what's necessary. Nothing more. If you can treat it, we'll tell you how. If we need to, we'll
          explain why and help you decide the next step.
        </p>
        <p>
          We aim to complete most things in one visit. Simple, straightforward care. We'll give you clear, simple advice
          to help you care for your teeth and avoid bigger issues down the road.
        </p>
      </section>

