        <p class="phone-number">+1 (610) 678-5700</p>
      </section>

      <!-- TREATMENT APPROACH SECTION -->
      <section id="treatment-approach">
        <h2>Treatment Approach</h2>
        <p>
          We treat what's necessary. Nothing more. If it's not a problem, we won't touch it. If home care can treat it,
          we'll give you a plan. And if it's serious, we'll explain why and how we'll treat it.
        </p>
        <p>
          Most treatments are handled in one visit. Fewer trips, more convenience. We'll help you build the right habits
          so you can take care of your teeth and avoid bigger issues down the road.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- OUR PROMISE SECTION -->
      <section id="our-promise">
        <h2>Our Promise</h2>
        <p>
          No judgment, no lectures. All respect. We don't know what's best for you. Only you do. We'll give you the
          facts and help guide you toward the right decision.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you need treatment, we'll tell you why. If you're not ready, that's fine too. We'll give you a plan and let
          you decide when it's right for you.
        </p>
        <p>We stick to <strong>clear, conservative care.</strong> The kind most people actually need.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="faq">
        <h2 class="centered-heading">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <details>
          <summary class="centered-text"><strong>Click to see 👀</strong></summary>
          <div class="faq-section">
            <hr style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #e5e5e5" />
            <p>
              <strong>When can I get an appointment?</strong><br />
              We try to get you in fast often the same day. If it's after hours, we'll follow up first thing in the
              morning.
            </p>
            <p>
              If you leave a message, send an email, or text, we'll get back to you as soon as we can. Sometimes we're
              with patients, but we do check everything regularly.
            </p>
            <p>
              If it's urgent and can't wait, use the emergency option on our phone line. That gets flagged for quicker
              attention.
            </p>

            <p>
              <strong>What if I'm nervous about dental work?</strong><br />
              Dental work doesn't have to be stressful. We'll walk you through every step and make sure you're good
              before we do anything.
            </p>

            <p>
              <strong>What if I need a root canal or crown?</strong><br />
              If you need more advanced care, we'll explain why, lay out the options, and let you decide. No stress. No
              pressure. Just facts.
            </p>

            <p>
              <strong>How do I know if my insurance covers this?</strong><br />
              We'll confirm your coverage before doing anything and handle the paperwork for you. No surprises.
            </p>

            <p>
              <strong>What if I don't have insurance?</strong><br />
              Doesn't matter. We'll go over your cost and any payment options upfront. Nothing starts until you're on
              board. No commitments without your go-ahead.
            </p>

            <p>
              <strong>Will you tell me my cost upfront?</strong><br />
              Always. No hidden fees. No guesswork. You'll know before we start.
            </p>

            <div class="cta-wrapper faq-cta-buttons">
              <a href="tel:+16106785700" class="cta" onclick="gtag('event', 'click_call_now');"> 📞 Call Now </a>
              <a href="sms:+16106785700" class="cta" onclick="gtag('event', 'click_text_now');"> 📱 Text Now </a>
            </div>

            <p class="faq-reassurance">No pressure. No confusion. Just straight-up care that makes sense.</p>
            <p class="faq-cta">Still got questions? Call or text. We'll make it easy.</p>
          </div>
